		"body": "<h2>Omote gyaku</h2>\n<p>(possilby inaccurate)</p>\n<p>Tori start in segan. uke punches left. Gedan uke left and move in punching with right to eyes, whilst still holding left. pivot your body 180 as you apply omote gyaku.</p>\n<h2>Ura gyaku</h2>\n<p>(possilby inaccurate)</p>\n<p>As above, but ura gyaku</p>\n<h2>Omote onikudaki</h2>\n<p>(Reach under on the outside of arm)</p>\n<p>Uke punches right. Gedan uke right. Uke punches left. Gedan uke left. Step in with your right hand under is arm you have just blocked and onikudaki.</p>\n<h2>Ura onikudaki</h2>\n<p>Uke punches right. Gedan uke right. Uke punches left. Gedan uke left. Then (step in - if needed and) a lightly haymaker-esque tsuki to the eyes. Keep the punch swinging around into the ura onikudaki position in his elbow pit. Clasp hands, hold his arms close to chest, row onikudaki.</p>\n<h2>Taki ori</h2>\n<p>Uke collar grab. take his hand with yours, fold his wrist and push it up high as you step in close to him. Change your grip on his hand to achive omote (outside/back of his hand to your palm) or ura (palm to palm)</p>\n<h2>Misc Move 1</h2>\n<p>Uke punch left. Gedan uke left. Uke punch right gedan uke right. Uke kick left. Keri kudai left (uke style with backhand). Uke kick right. Tsuki with left hand punches leg away. Then left hand does kung fu style backfist to face. End with either a) right hand punch to heart or b) turning armbar type throw, as yosi often does.</p>\n<h2>Misc Move 2</h2>\n<p>...ends with kick to his supporting leg to deaden it. go down on one knee and pivot to pull him around you and down.</p>\n<h2>Misc Move 3</h2>\n<p>(may be innaccurate)</p>\n<p>Uke punches right. Gedan uke right. Uke punches left. Gedan uke left. Pivot 180 degrees as you step in and grab ukes trapezius and bicep. Zenpo keri to his chest. Before your foot goes back down, twist and do a hook/kick to his back leg, lifting it up as you pull is arm down. This is a circular movement that should bring him down.</p>\n<h2>Misc Move 4</h2>\n<p>Kumiuchi. pull his collar across his throat as you pinch his adams apple and pull his other arm towards you. Ensuring he is bending over backwards will prevent him from walking backwards out of the technique. Have your legs behind his legs. Kick his leg out with ushiro keri.</p>",
