		"body": "<ul>\n<li>Lying on back to lying on front<ol>\n<li>Take him to the matt but keep one of his arms</li>\n<li>Be at his head end</li>\n<li>Place his elbow on your shin, rotate his arm, apply pressure</li>\n<li>Kneel on his back, put his folded hand against your chest</li>\n</ol></li>\n<li>Takeori</li>\n<li>Step through with shin, rest elbow on it. Pull hand backwards.</li>\n<li>As above, but reach through, grabbing his pectoral hard with a powerful renishi and and rest his elbow on your arm, pulling back for break</li>\n<li>Put his arm between your legs and roll</li>\n<li>Put armbar on and kneel on his head</li>\n</ul>",
