		"body": "<h2>Defense</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Dont let him get too close. Avoid messy grapple.</li>\n<li>Protect vulnerable areas with kamae.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Offense</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">Strong and accurate attacks</span></li>\n<li>Apply joint locks powerfully with speed and force</li>\n<li>Aim directly for head, neck, eyes, temple, back of head, heart, floating ribs</li>\n<li>Use on/off pain with locks and skin grabs etc</li>\n<li>Finishing techniques if necessary. i.e. hard chokes, stamps, arm breaks</li>\n</ul>",
