		"body": "<h2>Te Hodoki</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Mirror Grab\n<ul>\n<li>Step back into doko and rotate forearm to slip out. From here, armbar or onikudaki</li>\n<li>Step to be facing the same was as your attacker as you rotate forearm parallel to the ground and slip out. Then knee to kneepit, palm to chin.</li>\n<li>Aikido: Step to be facing opposite way of attacker, lift arm up, step through as you pirouette, bring arm down to throw.</li>\n<li>Kung fu: Dual Motion - jerk your captured arm away as you slide the hand of your other arm down forcefully, brushing ukes hand off</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Cross Grab\n<ul>\n<li>Make circular motion with trapped arm and push against back of their hand. Armbar etc.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Double Grab\n<ul>\n<li>Rotate arms in circle one way</li>\n<li>Rotate arms in circle the other way, smashing ukes hands together at the end. Then cast down and...Arm over back of neck and drop on head. Palm to chin. Head butt. Punch.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Double Grab on One Arm\n<ul>\n<li>Reach in and free hand and lever out</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Tai Hodoki</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>From behind\n<ul>\n<li>Inhale and make your chest big. Then suddenly exhale and make yourself small, slipping down and out</li>\n<li>Headbutt with the back of your head to the front of his</li>\n<li>Stamp on his foot</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>",
