		"body": "<h2><span style=\"font-size: 1.5em;\">Kata</span></h2>\n<p>All kata Tori has bo and Uke has Sword.</p>\n<h3>One</h3>\n<p>Ashi Bari left, Do Uchi left, Ashi Bari Right, Tento Uchi, Tsuki as you go down on one knee.&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Two</h3>\n<p>Tento Uchi. Tsuki, as you go down on one knee.</p>\n<h3>Three</h3>\n<p>Start in Jodan. Toggle into Ihen. Feign a small strike. Then swing the bo around overhead for Kasumi Uchi.</p>\n<h3>Four</h3>\n<p>Aggressive. Alternate each of the side of origin for each strike. Tento Uchi, Tento Uchi, Fein Tento Uchi but turn it into Do Uchi at last minute, Ashi Bari, Tento Uchi.</p>\n<div class=\"tips\">\n<h3>Tips</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Use the whole length of the bo. Use its length to your advantage. Really throw it out at the uke. One hand should be at the very end, the other, about a foot in front of it at the most.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
